data.title: Warner College of Natural Resources
data.text:
Warner College Dean’s List

Congratulations to the students on the Warner College Dean’s List

In order to be on the Dean’s List, students must maintain a 3.75 GPA or higher in at least 12 GPA related credits. Lists posted here are for the prior semester and are updated at the end of each semester.
